(3 comments)

Thanks Kairat for taking this on!

There is still similar cases at least in:
glance/common/utils.py (mutating())
glance/db/sqlalchemy/api.py (multiple)
glance/api/v2/image_data.py
glance/api/v3/artifacts.py (upload() except forbidden)

I also do think that we should honor pep8 and be consistent across our logging. If we do this for debug (which absolutely makes sense) we should do the same reformatting for the rest of the levels as well.
